    "message_id": "1000000",
    "reply_to_message_id": "",
    "text": "Toshio stopped by the studio this afternoon. Said the wood-ash glaze on the tea bowls is 'starting to speak.' Three years and that's the first time he's said anything approaching approval."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1781375400",
    "from_id": "1000000003",
    "message_id": "1000001",
    "reply_to_message_id": "",
    "text": "Three years!! That's huge. Is that his way of saying they're good or just... less bad?"
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1781375400",
    "from_id": "1000000001",
    "message_id": "1000002",
    "reply_to_message_id": "",
    "text": "Hard to say with him. He held one for about four minutes without speaking, which I've learned to read as good. Also asked about the next anagama firing."
  },
